INT. WILL'S PARENTS' HOUSE - NIGHT

Bedroom. Edward and Sandra ASLEEP. The phone RINGS once, then is picked up.

WILL (V.O.)
There are stories that are told over and over until they take on the shape of myth.

CUT TO:

EXT. CALLOWAY HOUSE - DAY

A vast estate. Spanish moss drapes ancient oaks.

YOUNG EDWARD
(softly)
This isn't a swamp. It's a kingdom.

JENNY ^
I never said it was.

